&lt;h3 id=&#34;blur-up-images&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#blur-up-images&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Blur Up Images&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Low resolution placeholder ie. the &amp;quot;blur up&amp;quot; technique. You can see this in action &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9hcHBlbHNpaW5pLm5ldC8yMDE3L3RyaWxhdGVyYXRpb24td2l0aC1uLXBvaW50cy8=&#34;&gt;in this blog entry&lt;/span&gt;. Scroll down to see blur up images.&lt;/p&gt;
