&lt;p&gt;Lazyloaded &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc21hc2hpbmdtYWdhemluZS5jb20vMjAxNC8wNS9yZXNwb25zaXZlLWltYWdlcy1kb25lLXJpZ2h0LWd1aWRlLXBpY3R1cmUtc3Jjc2V0Lw==&#34;&gt;Responsive images&lt;/span&gt; are supported via  &lt;code&gt;data-srcset&lt;/code&gt; . If browser does not support  &lt;code&gt;srcset&lt;/code&gt;  and there is no polyfill the image from  &lt;code&gt;data-src&lt;/code&gt;  will be shown.&lt;/p&gt;
